nload: nload (Monitors network traffic and bandwidth usage)
nload:
nload: nload is a console application which monitors network traffic and
nload: bandwidth usage in real time. It visualizes the in- and outgoing
nload: traffic using two graphs and provides additional info like total
nload: amount of transfered data and min/max network usage.
nload:
nload: http://www.roland-riegel.de/nload/
